PERSONAL NOTES

This was my first original material I made from scratch. Pretty proud of it. It's simple but effective. Cost almost nothing. Kids use it constantly.

Best part: I made it on a Sunday afternoon while watching football. Montessori prep doesn't have to be complicated.

